{"tid":1896242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「地平說」支持者乘自製火箭升空　最終墜毁加州沙漠身亡","createTime":"2020-02-25T04:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T04:48:07.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e740d6f48cd9d0a45fc20d572ba505b0fe89c9d8","tid":1896242,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"美國知名「地平說」支持者、業餘火箭發明家休斯（Mike Hughes），在當地時間上周六（22日）在加州乘坐自製的蒸汽推動的火箭升空，目的是證明「地平說」屬實，但火箭升空約半分鐘後失控墜毁於沙漠，休斯當場身亡，終年64歲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200224/s00005/1582539594518/「地平說」支持者乘自製火箭升空-半分鐘後墜毁加州沙漠身亡\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200224%2Fs00005%2F1582539594518%2F%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%B9%B3%E8%AA%AA%E3%80%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%80%85%E4%B9%98%E8%87%AA%E8%A3%BD%E7%81%AB%E7%AE%AD%E5%8D%87%E7%A9%BA-%E5%8D%8A%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%BE%8C%E5%A2%9C%E6%AF%81%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E6%B2%99%E6%BC%A0%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%A1&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=fcff9e38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200224%2Fs00005%2F1582539594518%2F%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%B9%B3%E8%AA%AA%E3%80%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%80%85%E4%B9%98%E8%87%AA%E8%A3%BD%E7%81%AB%E7%AE%AD%E5%8D%87%E7%A9%BA-%E5%8D%8A%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%BE%8C%E5%A2%9C%E6%AF%81%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E6%B2%99%E6%BC%A0%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%A1&h=bb59c8fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200224/s00005/1582539594518/「地平說」支持者乘自製火箭升空-半分鐘後墜毁加州沙漠身亡</a>"},{"pid":"fafe134a462eed5d100f8da3fe63a8cf8fa00dae","tid":1896242,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:34:21.000Z","msg":"外號「瘋狂邁克」的休斯，當日為一個科學頻道的節目《Homemade Astronauts》拍攝新系列影片，以記錄自製火箭愛好者升空的探索過程。休斯曾於2018年3月在該節目中成功利用自製火箭升上約570米高空，到達後他坐在駕駛艙內以降落傘着陸。他今次升空高度的目標為5000呎（約1552米），希望到達後會透過俯瞰地球以證明地球是平的。<br />\n<br />\n從影片可見，火箭升空後一瞬間，降落傘就意外拋出飄走，火箭繼續往上衝約20秒後開始失去動力，隨後墜毁在沙漠。該科學頻道發表聲明，向休斯的家人和朋友致哀，又稱這次發射是休斯的夢想。"},{"pid":"f88571fd2813171a64676bbf4afa5b804694ca08","tid":1896242,"uid":28831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"5000呎？<br />\n坐飛機都30000呎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36e8e0d2d2f64df71e9043efdf07d9ae47c4d0c","tid":1896242,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:36:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WE-_erpJ9Xo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWE-_erpJ9Xo&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=ecaadf03\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WE-_erpJ9Xo</a>"},{"pid":"acd1bba631a9e12242356e249fe1641b6d4eefaf","tid":1896242,"uid":16447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"飛得起其實都好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8263b920dda3dc23c09bf0ca51341c09f74d8b2c","tid":1896242,"uid":3747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"達爾文奬得奬者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf19457ebee20589ac46b59b2b646bfc730dd16","tid":1896242,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"其實比一百幾廿萬搵virgin就可以飛上太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8e052c2a0e018984313900f3ceab20634418e6","tid":1896242,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"蒸氣火箭係咩玩法"},{"pid":"56dc42d1db6153ed493672d79ac49e09eb0ad801","tid":1896242,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:48:07.000Z","msg":"一定係對家嘅陰謀<br />\n驚佢搵到證據<br />\n於是 喺火箭做手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}